title: Dinosaurs - Ocean Ave
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Catering, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has several vegan choices including a crispy shredded tofu sandwich with vegenaise, a roasted portobello sandwich, a tofu and taro salad and a vegan spring roll. Some juices and shakes are vegan as well. Basic sandwich shop with tables and chairs indoors and outdoors and a casual atmosphere. Also sells vegan staples such as fish sauce and condensed milk and offers catering. Part of a chain.
